title: Braun Series 9 - Design
description:
Braun Series 9 - World’s most efficient shaver*. Exceptionally gentle.
With SyncroSonic technology and a Titanium coated middle trimmer. Five specialized shaving elements capture more hair in one stroke for fewer strokes and less skin irritation.
SyncroSonic Technology
Our patented technology reads and automatically adapts to your beard.
